---
import '../styles/about.css';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" navbar={true}>
  <div class="title">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="about-us">
    <p>
      Welcome to CMK, your go-to destination for premium customized computer peripherals. 
      We specialize in tailoring keyboards and mice to suit your style, performance needs, 
      and comfort. Whether you are a gamer, designer, or office professional, we provide 
      high-quality, durable, and aesthetically crafted products to enhance your experience.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      At CMK, our mission is to revolutionize the way you interact with your computer. 
      We believe that every individual has unique preferences, and our goal is to offer 
      custom solutions that elevate comfort, efficiency, and performance. We aim to empower 
      gamers, creatives, and professionals by providing high-quality peripherals that are 
      designed for excellence.
    </p>
    
    <h2>What We Offer</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Fully customizable mechanical keyboards with switch and keycap options</li>
      <li>Personalized gaming mice with ergonomic enhancements</li>
      <li>RGB lighting and software customization for an immersive experience</li>
      <li>Premium materials ensuring durability and longevity</li>
      <li>Exclusive limited-edition designs and collaborations</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Why Choose CMK?</h2>
    <p>
      Our commitment to quality sets us apart. Every product we create undergoes rigorous 
      testing to ensure superior performance and longevity. We use only the finest materials 
      to deliver peripherals that offer both style and function.
    </p>
    <p>
      Customer satisfaction is our top priority. Our team of experts is always ready to 
      assist you with personalized recommendations and support, ensuring a seamless 
      customization experience.
    </p>

    <h2>Join the CMK Community</h2>
    <p>
      Beyond just products, CMK is a growing community of tech enthusiasts who share a passion 
      for innovation and customization. Join us on our journey by following us on social media, 
      participating in our exclusive events, and staying updated on our latest designs.
    </p>

    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>
      Have questions or need help selecting the perfect setup? Contact our team today! 
      We're here to bring your vision to life with customized peripherals that match 
      your personality and needs.
    </p>
    <a href="/contact" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><button>Get in Touch</button></a>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .title {
    margin-top: 5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .title h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .about-us {
    margin-top: 5rem;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
    text-align: center;
    width: 70%;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;

  }
  .about-us p {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #e7dcdc;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .about-us h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    color: #f4f4f4;
  }
  .about-us ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .about-us ul li {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem; /* Increased space for the checkmark */
  }
  .about-us ul li::before {
    content: 'âœ”';
    color: #27ae60;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 1.5rem; /* Adjust the size of the checkmark */
  }
  .about-us button {
    background-color: #ffcc0000;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: #27ae60 2px solid;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .about-us button:hover {
    background-color: #27ae60;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(39, 174, 96, 0.7); 

  }
  /* Scoll fix */
  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}
html, body {
    height: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    overflow-y: auto; /* Ensures vertical scrolling is enabled */
  }
  
  .container {
    min-height: 100vh; /* Ensures the container takes up full viewport height */
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px;
  }
</style>
